/**
 * The Riiak extension for Yii allows you to connect to a Riak instance,
 * create, modify, and delete Riak objects, add and remove links from
 * Riak objects, run Javascript (and
 * Erlang) based Map/Reduce operations, and run Linkwalking
 * operations.
 * 
 * Based on Riak PHP client by Basho, created by Rusty Klophaus (@rklophaus) (rusty@basho.com)
 * 
 * @author Jon Langevin (@intel352) <jon@phpsitesolutions.com>
 * @package Riiak
 */